           }
         }
     ]
@@ -250,7 +250,7 @@
             </div>
             <div class="faq__item">
               <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">Can I do laser if I'm on my period?</button>
-              <div class="faq__answer"><p>Yes. Some women find sensitivity slightly higher during their period, but there's no safety issue.</p></div>
+              <div class="faq__answer"><p>Yes — there is no safety issue. Pain-research literature suggests pain sensitivity can vary somewhat across the menstrual cycle, but findings aren't consistent enough to say a period makes laser more painful. See our <a href="/blog/laser-hair-removal-during-period-pain-evidence">evidence review</a> for the research.</p></div>
